Class AccessPoint

java.lang.Object
  com.lows.AccessPoint

public class AccessPoint
extends java.lang.Object

The class that stores all Access Point parameters, an List of this class is used to store the current IEEE 802.11 scan results. TODO: -add an timestamp field, when this entry was stored.
